description: Updates the image tag mutability settings for the specified repository. For more information, see Image tag mutability in the Amazon Elastic Container Registry User Guide.

parameters.name: repositoryName
parameters.description: The name of the repository in which to update the image tag mutability settings.

parameters.name: imageTagMutability
parameters.description: The tag mutability setting for the repository. If MUTABLE is specified, image tags can be overwritten. If IMMUTABLE is specified, all image tags within the repository will be immutable which will prevent them from being overwritten.

nested_items.name: registryId
nested_items.description: The registry ID associated with the request.

nested_items.name: repositoryName
nested_items.description: The repository name associated with the request.

nested_items.name: imageTagMutability
nested_items.description: The image tag mutability setting for the repository.
